        <sponsor name-id="S326">Mr. Udall of New Mexico</sponsor> (for himself, <cosponsor name-id="S347">Mr. Moran</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S321">Mr. Johanns</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSGA00">Committee on Homeland Security and Governmental Affairs</committee-name>
